<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: archogenetics -->
  <Archogenetics.label>アルコ遺伝学</Archogenetics.label>
  <!-- EN: Allows a gene assembler to use archite capsules to create seemingly impossible genes. Archite genes and archite capsules can be obtained from traders. -->
  <Archogenetics.description>遺伝子アセンブラがアルカイトカプセルを使用し,一見不可能とも思えるような遺伝子を作成できるようにします.アルカイト遺伝子とアルカイトカプセルはトレーダーから入手できます.</Archogenetics.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->archogenetics</li>
    <li>subject_story->excavated archite genes from the transcendent moon of Ix</li>
    <li>subject_story->made a good living as an archite gene trader</li>
    <li>subject_story->led a research expedition to an ancient monolith and returned changed</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->assembling archite genes</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->creating seemingly impossible genes</li>
  -->
  <Archogenetics.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->アルコ遺伝学</li>
    <li>subject_story->巨大コンピューター惑星の第九衛星からアルカイトの遺伝子を発掘した</li>
    <li>subject_story->アルカイト遺伝子トレーダーとして豊かな生計を立てた</li>
    <li>subject_story->遠征調査隊を率いて古代のモノリスへと向かい,戻ってきたときには別の姿になっていた</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->アルカイト遺伝子の作成</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->超常的な遺伝子作成</li>
  </Archogenetics.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: deathrest -->
  <Deathrest.label>死眠</Deathrest.label>
  <!-- EN: Those with the deathrest gene must periodically undergo a special deathrest coma that lasts several days. This research project allows you to construct buildings which accelerate the deathrest coma and confer specific bonuses on the deathrester. Over time, you can build a grand deathrest temple. -->
  <Deathrest.description>死眠遺伝子を持つ者は,数日間続く特殊な死眠という昏睡を定期的に行わなければなりません.この研究計画は,死眠による昏睡を短縮し,死眠者に特殊効果を与える設備を建設できるようにします.時間をかければ壮大な死眠の寺院を建設できます.</Deathrest.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->deathrest</li>
    <li>subject_story->dissected corpses from a deathrest temple, finally understanding how it worked</li>
    <li>subject_story->interviewed a celebrity who never seemed to age, eventually learning her secrets</li>
    <li>subject_story->attempted to replicate the technology and fell into a coma, only to wake weeks later</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing deathrest facilities</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->improving deathrest</li>
  -->
  <Deathrest.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->死眠</li>
    <li>subject_story->死眠用の部屋に残された死体を解剖し,設備の仕組みを理解した</li>
    <li>subject_story->老いを全く感じさせないとある有名人に取材を行い,そこで彼女の秘密を知った</li>
    <li>subject_story->技術の再現を試みた.しかしその結果,昏睡状態に陥り,目が覚めたのは数週間後だった</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->死眠用施設の建築</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->死眠の改善</li>
  </Deathrest.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: fertility procedures -->
  <FertilityProcedures.label>生殖制御</FertilityProcedures.label>
  <!-- EN: Perform the surgeries necessary to create a test tube embryo from a fertile man and woman, then implant the embryo in a surrogate mother or growth vat. Also, perform sterilization surgeries on men and women. -->
  <FertilityProcedures.description>繁殖可能な男女に手術を行い試験管受精卵を作成し,代理母,もしくは人工生育槽に移植します.また,男女の避妊手術を行えるようになります.</FertilityProcedures.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->fertility procedures</li>
    <li>subject_story->helped families in the coreworlds achieve their dream of parenthood with test-tube embryos</li>
    <li>subject_story->saved the rare Callopian boomrat from extinction with dangerous hand-fertilization techniques</li>
    <li>subject_story->solved the population crisis on an urbworld with fertility interventions and growth vats</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->altering human fertility</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->improving or blocking human fertility</li>
  -->
  <FertilityProcedures.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->生殖制御</li>
    <li>subject_story->Coreworldに住むとある夫婦の,試験管胚を使って子供を作るという夢を叶えられるよう支援した</li>
    <li>subject_story->カロピアに生息するボムネズミの希少種を,手作業による危険な受精技術で絶滅の危機から救った</li>
    <li>subject_story->Urbworldの人口問題を解決する手段として不妊治療と人工生育槽を利用した</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->生殖機能の改変</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->生殖機能の制御</li>
  </FertilityProcedures.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
